[link: /commands/categories/bytes.md] ’Щ@0d9689124829970fc8636bf2c66f75e8e9dddaf8917263233413c857a14280efЩaTitle: title: bytes remove
Path: Signature
Content:
``> bytes remove {flags} (pattern) ...rest``
’Щ@15fd1860180a5c83c360e37c5f0f3ba6097daa561ed7a34faa42606afd0c1fcfЩ‘Title: title: bytes remove
Path: Flags
Content:
``--end, -e``
: Remove from end of binary.
``--all, -a``
: Remove occurrences of finding binary.
’Щ@3645ef73dfb99c03f06ab58fa8a230c7c5cda63b8e8e617a5ca95d1496a543dcЩІTitle: title: bytes remove
Path: Parameters
Content:
``pattern``
: The pattern to find.
``...rest``
: For a data structure input, remove bytes from data at the given cell paths.
